Package mini_game

Class Summary
MiniGame The classes from the mini_game package, including this class, provide a framework for making a Swing based game.
MiniGameDataModel This class provides the base class for a game data management class.
MiniGameEventRelayer Some basic event handling is provided by this class for this framework.
MiniGameTimerTask This simple class serves as the task executed each frame for updating, and then rendering the game.
Sprite Sprite objects represent a visible game entity, which may be a game character, enemy, or button.
SpriteType A SpriteType describes a particular type of Sprite.
